<item>
            <title>[KAFKA-1356] Topic metadata requests takes too long to process</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/KAFKA-1356</link>
                <project id="12311720" key="KAFKA">Kafka</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Currently we&apos;re seeing slow response times in handling get topic metadata requests.&lt;/p&gt;

